{"tid":2418187,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡志偉三高受控制 多謝石牆花支援","createTime":"2021-02-22T12:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:17:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b82c4d188dfe881fe67231d7ac29d37bad67a8d1","tid":2418187,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vDX-lley3V6VagAQ55w8LH2ikl4=/802x776/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y43EXPTEVZGA3HC332MJ7XBX7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvDX-lley3V6VagAQ55w8LH2ikl4%3D%2F802x776%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY43EXPTEVZGA3HC332MJ7XBX7I.jpg&h=a3a6de09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為違反保釋條件而被還押嘅民主黨前主席胡志偉，早前趁農曆年三十晚喺獄中寫信畀前同事、前社福界立法會議員邵家臻，首先自爆因為規律作息、控制飲食、早睡早起，原來嘅三高問題似乎都被控制喺安全水平。<br />\n<br />\n長期抗爭下，身心靈都好緊要，志偉多謝阿臻創辦嘅「石牆花」來信打氣，為佢帶嚟「吾道不孤」嘅支持，亦都多謝對方同一眾爭取囚權朋友嘅努力，換嚟佢喺獄中嘅待遇。<br />\n<br />\n志偉話，面對專權從來都要小心翼翼咁尋找對策，但係總原則係「永不放棄」，佢形容石牆花生長喺貧瘠環境，但強大嘅生命力同堅持信念，必定會有開花結果嘅日子。<br />\n<br />\n正月未過，北京又吹來暴風，睇返年三十晚寫信嘅志偉嘅說話，可能會有返啲安慰，佢話儘管黎明前嘅黑暗仍然令人透唔到氣，但光明必現，寄語大家加油，願好人一生平安，亦希望「牆裏牆外心連心，花落花開善惡到頭終有報」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/P3VHXHFFSVCLZCWEPRS76AKY2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FP3VHXHFFSVCLZCWEPRS76AKY2I%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XhQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=fb447b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FP3VHXHFFSVCLZCWEPRS76AKY2I%2F&h=38f03892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/P3VHXHFFSVCLZCWEPRS76AKY2I/</a>"},{"pid":"3dd5da67c20ad155cf3dbc4e2086eb131ada5607","tid":2418187,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k